        </item>
        <item>
            <title>MG 高达维度尔 + HG 白骑士开箱</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/30/mgvidar/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mgvidar</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/30/mgvidar/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 10:20:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1300221</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<h2>MG 高达维度尔</h2><p>MG 高达维度尔 ASW-G-XX Gundam Vidar，是属于《机动战士高达，铁血的孤儿》第二季的机体，现已推出，立即为大家开箱看看。在动画中，高达维度尔由盖利欧·鲍德温（Gaelio Bauduin）驾驶，该角色采用「维度尔」作为化名，象征北欧神话中的复仇之神。其原型为受损的高达基马利斯（Gundam Kimaris Trooper），在月球外轨道联合舰队（Arianrhod Fleet）的改装下，成为具备更高战斗力的机体。设计师形部一平参与了机体的监修，确保模型与动画设定一致。</p><p><a title="_DSC9084" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419218954/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419218954_009b5c7253_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9084" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300228" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/gundam_vidar_by_inno-694x422.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="422" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/gundam_vidar_by_inno-694x422.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/gundam_vidar_by_inno.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300229" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ezgif85b0a748dd7376.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="513" /></p><p>模型的高达框架有修改过，肩关节的活动范围显著提升，适合模拟动画中的战斗姿势。脚部的猎刃可展开，增加机动感的视觉效果，而膝部装甲与推进器的同步移动确保了腿部弯曲时的流畅性与真实感。手枪的 blowback movement 是 MG 系列的可动机构设计，而步枪的弹匣可拆卸，允许玩家模拟装填或更换弹药的场景。突击军刀则配有可替换的刀刃零件，能重现动画中脱离刀鞘的状态，细节精致。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="_DSC9086" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270258/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270258_1ebb8acd4b_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9086" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9088" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54418161872/